<strong>
<b>Can’t find what you are looking for?</b></strong><p><strong>
There are a number of courses offered this semester through the Russian Exchange. These courses are taught through distance-learning options by our partner institutions. There are no additional fees charged. You may enroll in these classes by going to the <a href="http://online.northcarolina.edu/unconline/exdetails.php?exid=2" target="_blank">Russian Exchange</a>. Please contact Dr. Raymond Burt, chair of foreign languages, at 962-4095 for additional information or questions.
</strong>
